/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chrissy-teigen-selena-gomez@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>克里斯西·泰根（Chrissy Teigen）在白宫对最近移民袭击的帖子的回应后，来到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/selena-gomez">赛琳娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）</a>的防守。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/emilia-perez-review-zoe-saldana-selena-gomez-flawed-musical-melodrama-3805570">“ Emilia Perez”评论：ZoeSaldaña和Selena Gomez放开了有缺陷的音乐情节剧</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周（1月27日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/selena-gomez-breaks-down-while-reacting-to-trumps-deportation-of-immigrants-all-my-people-are-getting-attacked-3832513"><em>艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez）的</em>明星和歌手赛琳娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）发表了一个Instagram故事</a>，录音自己的泪水说：“我所有的人都在受到攻击……孩子们。我不明白。我很抱歉。我希望我能做些什么，但我不能。我不知道该怎么办。我保证，我会尽一切努力。” </p><figure id="attachment_3821420" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821420" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821420" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp